09:23.130 --> 09:25.833
- [sighs]

09:25.866 --> 09:27.234
Did she ever mention
the name of the guy

09:27.267 --> 09:31.038
at the--
the admissions office?

09:31.071 --> 09:34.808
- No, she never mentioned it.

09:34.842 --> 09:37.244
Do you think she...

09:37.277 --> 09:40.247
that because of our fight,
she took all those pills?

09:40.280 --> 09:44.017
- No.
No, put that out of your head.

09:44.051 --> 09:46.219
I think she loves you
very much,

09:46.253 --> 09:49.322
and it's because of that she's
gonna make a full recovery.

09:49.356 --> 09:51.992
*

09:52.025 --> 09:53.226
Come on.

09:53.260 --> 09:54.828
- You got to hit
that thing harder, man.

09:54.862 --> 09:56.263
- You know what's overrated?

09:56.296 --> 09:59.132
Wireless,
and putting lemon in water.

09:59.166 --> 10:00.267
I don't get that.

10:00.300 --> 10:01.501
All right.

10:01.534 --> 10:04.071
So Justin says that his mother
was spending time with some guy

10:04.104 --> 10:05.305
who works in the office
of admissions

10:05.338 --> 10:07.007
of Hudson University.

10:07.040 --> 10:11.044
I got 27 males
in that department, 19 women.

10:11.078 --> 10:13.046
- Takes all those people
to look at applications

10:13.080 --> 10:13.881
