10:28.929 --> 10:30.931
Director of Admissions.

10:36.036 --> 10:38.371
- Alden Kessler.
Where is he?

10:38.405 --> 10:39.873
Thanks.

10:42.943 --> 10:44.177
Hey, where's Alden Kessler?

10:44.211 --> 10:46.947
- You're looking at him.

10:46.980 --> 10:49.216
- Wait, you're Alden Kessler?
- Is there a problem?

10:49.249 --> 10:51.919
- Yeah.
A tall white one.

10:51.952 --> 10:53.987
Do you know him?
Or her?

10:54.021 --> 10:55.188
- No.
Never seen either one.

10:55.222 --> 10:57.290
Look, what's going on here?
- This is Detective Carisi.

10:57.324 --> 10:58.391
I'm Detective Rollins.

10:58.425 --> 11:00.060
We're from
the Special Victims Unit

11:00.093 --> 11:03.363
and we're investigating
a rape allegation.

11:03.396 --> 11:05.833
Is that your signature?

11:05.866 --> 11:09.069
- No, and I've never set foot
in the Luxembourg Hotel. Why?

11:09.102 --> 11:12.405
- There's a rapist out there
pretending to be you.

11:12.439 --> 11:15.408
[dramatic music]

11:21.882 --> 11:22.015
.

11:22.049 --> 11:23.116
- We think someone is using
your name, your identity.

11:24.818 --> 11:26.353
Any idea why somebody
would want to do that?

11:26.386 --> 11:29.056
- This woman, Laura, does she
have a child applying to Hudson?

11:29.089 --> 11:32.860
- Yeah, her son.
Justin Collett.

11:32.893 --> 11:34.995
[keys clacking]

11:36.196 --> 11:38.365
- [sighs]

11:38.398 --> 11:41.869
Yeah, there he is.
Senior at York Prep.

11:41.902 --> 11:44.872
3.9 GPA, 2250 SAT scores.

11:44.905 --> 11:46.073
- That's good, right?
- Exceptional.

11:46.106 --> 11:49.877
Problem is, we get 2,000 kids
with similar credentials.

11:49.910 --> 11:51.211
We only accept 400.

11:51.244 --> 11:54.014
The other spots
go to international students,

11:54.047 --> 11:55.182
athletes,
diversity candidates.

11:55.215 --> 11:57.885
- So, tough to be a rich,
white kid with great grades?

11:57.918 --> 11:59.186
That--that's what
you're saying?

11:59.219 --> 12:01.054
- At elite universities, anyway.

12:01.088 --> 12:04.157
- That must make you
a pretty popular man, right?

12:04.191 --> 12:06.126
