the--the doorman

12:06.159 --> 12:08.228
for the most exclusive club
in the world.

12:08.261 --> 12:09.529
- Do any of these rich parents

12:09.562 --> 12:12.933
ever try to, um...
influence your decision?

12:12.966 --> 12:15.803
- [scoffs]
No, never.

12:15.836 --> 12:17.838
