12:19.907 --> 12:22.976
- Do any of them offer sex?
- Excuse me?

12:23.010 --> 12:26.413
- What I mean is, if you wanted
to exploit your power

12:26.446 --> 12:28.982
in a sexual way,
would there be any takers?

12:29.016 --> 12:31.184
- I've been offered all kinds
of outrageous things,

12:31.218 --> 12:34.988
a part ownership at a winery
in Bordeaux, a Monet.

12:35.022 --> 12:38.191
Last year, a hedge funder
with an underachieving son

12:38.225 --> 12:39.326
offered me $5 million,

12:39.359 --> 12:43.430
and yes, on occasion,
there have been sexual advances.

12:44.531 --> 12:45.799
- Laura Collett just woke up.

12:45.833 --> 12:48.001
Benson's on her way
to the hospital.

12:48.035 --> 12:51.238
Mr. Kessler, thank you.
We'll be in touch.

12:51.271 --> 12:53.540
- We, uh, we met on campus.

12:53.573 --> 12:56.009
Justin and I had just, uh,
taken a tour,

12:56.043 --> 12:58.545
and I was--I was getting coffee
at the café,

12:58.578 --> 13:02.449
and he, um...
he introduced himself to me.

13:02.482 --> 13:05.052
He said he worked
at the admissions office.

13:05.085 --> 13:08.055
- The night that you two were
at the Luxembourg Hotel,

13:08.088 --> 13:12.492
you sent him a text
that said, "Best sex ever."

13:12.525 --> 13:16.029
And then ten minutes later, you
sent him another text that said,

13:16.063 --> 13:19.032
"You raped me.
Burn in hell."

13:19.066 --> 13:21.168
So can you tell me what happened
in those ten minutes?

13:21.201 --> 13:24.004
- I figured out
he wasn't Alden Kessler.

13:24.037 --> 13:25.472
- How?

13:25.505 --> 13:27.040
- He mixed up
a few statistics.

13:27.074 --> 13:29.509
He said, um...

13:29.542 --> 13:32.179
said the endowment
was 9 billion.

13:32.212 --> 13:33.981
It's actually 13.

13:34.014 --> 13:35.182
- You got suspicious?

13:35.215 --> 13:37.050
- Yeah.

13:37.084 --> 13:39.586
- Had you Googled him or,
you know, looked him up?

13:39.619 --> 13:41.054
- I did,
and there he was

13:41.088 --> 13:44.491
on some professor's
Instagram page.

13:44.524 --> 13:47.928
